 <PERSON> Larry </PERSON> <PERSON> Thorson </PERSON> is <LOCATION> Asia </LOCATION> news editor of The <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION>.
