 expansion during the past five years Park officials said it was impossible to determine the amount of time a specific ranger or other employee might spend on a horse-related project. `` You see the horse program growing and growing and growing, and everything else going down hill,'' said park administrative officer <PERSON> Jane </PERSON> <PERSON> Becker </PERSON>. `` You see things falling apart, you must ask where is the money going.''
